      </p>
    </introduction>
        <task>
          <statement>
            <p>
              Show that <m>\{A_{a,b} \mid a, b \in \Z, b \neq 0\}</m> is a basis for a topology <m>\tau</m> on <m>\Z</m>.
              
            </p>
          </statement>
          <hint>
                <p>
                  If <m>B_1 = A_{a_1,b_1}</m> and <m>B_2 = A_{a_2,b_2}</m>,
