    </introduction>
        <task>
          <statement>
            <p>
              The set <m>\{\emptyset, \{a,b\}, \{a,b,d,f\}, \{d,f\},X\}</m> is a topology on the set <m>X = \{a,b,c,d,e,f\}</m>.
            </p>
          </statement>
        </task>
        <task>
          <statement>
